---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Privacy Policy - Camilo Pires"
  description="Privacy Policy for Camilo Pires' portfolio website. Learn how we collect, use, and protect your information when you visit our site."
  type="website"
  tags={["Privacy Policy", "Data Protection", "GDPR", "Cookies", "Personal Data"]}
>
  <Header />
  
  <main id="main-content">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="pt-24 pb-16 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          How I collect, use, and protect your information
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Privacy Policy Content -->
  <section class="py-16 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
          <strong>Last updated:</strong> {new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}
        </p>

        <div class="space-y-8">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">1. Introduction</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              This Privacy Policy describes how I collect, use, and protect your information when you visit 
              my portfolio website (camilopires.co.uk). I am committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring 
              the security of your personal information.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">2. Information I Collect</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              When you visit my website, I may collect the following types of information:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 space-y-2">
              <li><strong>Contact Information:</strong> Name, email address, and message content when you use the contact form</li>
              <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Information about how you interact with the website, including pages visited and time spent</li>
              <li><strong>Technical Information:</strong> Browser type, operating system, IP address, and device information</li>
              <li><strong>Cookies:</strong> Small data files stored on your device to improve your browsing experience</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">3. How I Use Your Information</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              I use the collected information for the following purposes:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 space-y-2">
              <li>Respond to your inquiries and provide customer support</li>
              <li>Improve website functionality and user experience</li>
              <li>Analyse website usage and performance</li>
              <li>Send important updates about my services (with your consent)</li>
              <li>Comply with legal obligations</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">4. Information Sharing</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              I do not sell, trade, or rent your personal information to third parties. I may share your information only in the following circumstances:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 space-y-2">
              <li>With your explicit consent</li>
              <li>To comply with legal obligations</li>
              <li>To protect my rights and safety</li>
              <li>With service providers who assist in website operation (under strict confidentiality agreements)</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">5. Data Security</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              I implement appropriate security measures to protect your personal information against 
              unauthorised access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction. However, no method of 
              transmission over the internet is 100% secure, and I cannot guarantee absolute security.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">6. Your Rights</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              You have the following rights regarding your personal information:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 space-y-2">
              <li><strong>Access:</strong> Request a copy of your personal data</li>
              <li><strong>Correction:</strong> Update or correct your information</li>
              <li><strong>Deletion:</strong> Request deletion of your personal data</li>
              <li><strong>Portability:</strong> Export your data in a standard format</li>
              <li><strong>Opt-out:</strong> Unsubscribe from communications</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">7. Cookies</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              This website uses cookies to improve your browsing experience. You can control cookie 
              settings through your browser preferences. Disabling cookies may affect website functionality.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">8. Third-Party Services</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              This website may use third-party services (such as analytics tools) that collect 
              information about your usage. These services have their own privacy policies, 
              and I encourage you to review them.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
              I may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. I will notify you of any changes 
              by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page and updating the "Last updated" date. 
              I encourage you to review this Privacy Policy periodically.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">10. Contact Information</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or my data practises, please contact me at:
            </p>
            <div class="bg-gray-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
              <p class="text-gray-700">
                <strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:dev@camilopires.co.uk" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">dev@camilopires.co.uk</a><br>
                <strong>Website:</strong> <a href="/" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">camilopires.co.uk</a>
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">11. Project-Specific Privacy Policies</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
              Some of my projects have their own specific privacy policies:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-gray-600 space-y-2">
              <li><a href="/projects/boxingscorecard-privacy" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">Boxing Scorecard Privacy Policy</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Back to Portfolio -->
  <section class="py-12 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700 font-semibold">
        ‚Üê Back to Portfolio
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
